   ROME
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
THE OVEN at Nuova Samim's lead smelter at Portovesme, Italy, shut down for
routine maintenance in mid-March, is scheduled to resume operations by April
24, a representative of the state-owned energy group Ente Nazionale
