<BYLINE>
   By BRUCE JACQUES
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
BTR Nylex, the Melbourne-based industrial conglomerate which is part of the
UK industrial group BTR, has confirmed a bid worth almost ADollars 80m for
Westinghouse Brake and Signal Australia, writes Bruce Jacques.
</TEXT>
<PUB>The Financial Times
