FT  10 APR 92 / UK Company News: Rathbone tops Pounds 3m with 22% increase
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Rathbone Brothers, the USM-traded asset management and private banking
group, increased pre-tax profit by 22 per cent in 1991. and is raising the
dividend by 25 per cent.
From turnover 11 per cent up to Pounds 11.4m, profit came to Pounds 3.12m
(Pounds 2.56m) and earnings per share worked through at 26.61p (22.11p). The
