   By REUTERS
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
   Kuala Lumpur
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
MALAYSIA'S public offer of 240.12m shares of Tenaga Nasional, the
state-owned electricity monopoly, at MDollars 4.50 each was oversubscribed
3.47 times, Reuter reports from Kuala Lumpur.
