considering the size of the issue.'
Another 60m shares were offered to locals and foreigners under a tender
system. These were oversubscribed 6.47 times with the highest bid at
MDollars 7.10 per share. A further 84.93m were offered to Tenaga employees
while 300m were alloted to approved Bumiputra investors.
